      "text": "\nShared purpose and values are essential to the coherence and vitality of a commons. A matrix of living meaning can only arise if it is actively embraced and lived by commoners; it cannot simply be declared or formally imposed. Therein lies the challenge: to consciously enact the practices that can intensify share purpose & values."
